de.fha.dpmi.modeling.bpmn

Interface BpmnModel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Model
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BpmnModelImpl

    public interface BpmnModel
extends Model
    Representation of a BPMN model. It constructs, stores and retrieves all model elements.
